      "parameters": {
        "language": "python",
        "pythonCode": "product_description = _('Analyze image').item.json.content\nuser_instructions = _('Telegram Trigger').item.json.message.caption\n\nprompt = f\"\"\"\nCreate video prompts for 3 connected scenes.\n\nCRITICAL - EXACT PRODUCT DETAILS FROM REFERENCE IMAGE:\n{product_description}\n\nYOU MUST use these EXACT product details in ALL 3 scenes:\n- Same product color\n- Same packaging design\n- Same brand text\n- Same product type\nDO NOT change or invent ANY product details.\n\nUser's scene instructions:\n{user_instructions}\n\nLANGUAGE REQUIREMENT: All dialogue must be in ENGLISH only.\n\nGenerate 3 progressive scenes with the EXACT SAME product shown in the reference image above.\n\"\"\"\n\nreturn {'chatInput': prompt}"
      },
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.code",
      "typeVersion": 2,
      "position": [
